OL,3,C'I had to tell my Dad he had cancer':
OL,4,CDeaf patients let down by NHS shortages
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports correspondent Mel
OL,7,FBarham speaks to those affected by the
OL,8,Fshortage of sign language interpreters
OL,9,Fin the NHS
OL,11,FPeople with hearing loss are putting
OL,12,Ftheir lives at risk, avoiding calling
OL,13,Fambulances or going to casualty
OL,14,Fbecause they can't make themselves
OL,15,Funderstood in an emergency.
