OL,3,C'I had to tell my Dad he had cancer':
OL,4,CDeaf patients let down by NHS shortages
OL,6,FCrystal Rolfe from the charity says it
OL,7,Fis a breach of equality and human
OL,8,Frights laws.
OL,10,F"One in four people have not taken
OL,11,Faction on a health condition, and
OL,12,Fabout half of British Sign Language
OL,13,Fusers have gone home from the doctor
OL,14,Fand not understood their diagnoses or
OL,15,Fhow to take their medicine or what
OL,16,Ftreatments they should be using," she
OL,17,Fsays.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
